CAPITALISTIC BEHAVIOR: IS IT AN EXERCISE IN GREED OR BRILLIANCE? 
True capitalism demands that all human interaction be conducted on a voluntary 
basis, appealing to the judgment of men, instead of on a mandatory basis, 
depending on the subjugation of men. It is a moral system. Let's stop feeling 
guilty about our new CD or the human freedom that created it. 
CASEY FAHY 
La Canada 
